belongs_to_collection.name: I Got Five on It Collection

overview: Jimmy and his friends are on a serious mission to party. But in their desperate pursuit of a good time, they are led on a wild cross-town series of hilarious misadventures where they get dissed and ripped off and doused by one seriously nasty towel. These guys want to be players but their more like water boys. You won't stop laughing as these guys go on the most hilarious road trip ever.
title: I Got Five on It
